ifferent frontend UI frameworks </p></div><!-- Features Section --><div class="_mb6_b6e01e"><h2 class="_sectionTitle_b6e01e">Basic Examples</h2><div class="_grid_b6e01e _grid3_b6e01e"><a class="_card_b6e01e _cardHover_b6e01e _linkCard_b6e01e" href="/examples/static"><div class="_textCenter_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">📄</div><h3 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Static Page</h3><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Pure static HTML page, no client-side JavaScript required </p></div></a><a class="_card_b6e01e _cardHover_b6e01e _linkCard_b6e01e" href="/examples/params/web-widget"><div class="_textCenter_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">🎯</div><h3 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Dynamic Routing</h3><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> File-system-based dynamic route handling </p></div></a><a class="_card_b6e01e _cardHover_b6e01e _linkCard_b6e01e" href="/examples/fetch"><div class="_textCenter_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">🔄</div><h3 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Data Fetching</h3><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Fetch data on the server and render as static HTML </p></div></a><a class="_card_b6e01e _cardHover_b6e01e _linkCard_b6e01e" href="/examples/action"><div class="_textCenter_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">⚡</div><h3 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Server Actions</h3><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Call server-side functions directly from the client </p></div></a><a class="_card_b6e01e _cardHover_b6e01e _linkCard_b6e01e" href="/examples/frameworks"><div class="_textCenter_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">🍀</div><h3 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Widgets</h3><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> React and Vue components work seamlessly on the same page </p></div></a><a class="_card_b6e01e _cardHover_b6e01e _linkCard_b6e01e" href="/examples/middleware"><div class="_textCenter_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">🧅</div><h3 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Middleware</h3><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Control requests and responses, and modify page metadata </p