"<!doctype html>
    <html lang="en">
      <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" /><title >Server Actions - Web Widget</title><style >web-widget{display:contents}</style><script type="module" src="/@vite/client"></script><script type="module" src="/entry.client.ts"></script><script type="server:context">{"pathname":"/examples/action","params":{}}</script>
      </head>
      <body>
        <!--[--><a href="#main-content" class="skip-link"> Skip navigation, go to main content </a><header class="_header_408c0a"><div class="_headerContent_408c0a"><div class="_brandLogo_408c0a"><a class="_brandText_408c0a" href="/"> Web Widget </a><div class="_techStackBadge_408c0a"><span class="_techText_408c0a">Vue Example</span></div></div><nav class="_navigation_08e302" aria-label="Main navigation" role="navigation"><button class="_mobileMenuButton_08e302" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobile-navigation-menu" aria-label="Open navigation menu"><span class="_hamburgerIcon_08e302"><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span></span></button><ul id="mobile-navigation-menu" class="_navigationMenu_08e302" role="list" aria-hidden="true"><!--[--><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples" class="" aria-label="Home">Home</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/static" class="" aria-label="Static Page">Static Page</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/params/web-widget" class="" aria-label="Dynamic Routing">Dynamic Routing</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/fetch" class="" aria-label="Data Fetching">Data Fetching</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/action" class="" aria-label="Server Actions">Server Actions</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/frameworks" class="" aria-label="Widgets">Widgets</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/middleware" class="" aria-label="Middleware">Middleware</a></li><!--]--></ul><!-- Mobile menu background overlay --><!----></nav></div></header><main id="main-content" class="_main_408c0a" tabindex="-1"><!--[--><div class="_container_b6e01e"><h1 class="_pageTitle_b6e01e">⚡ Server Actions</h1><div class="_highlight_b6e01e _info_b6e01e"><h2>Call server-side functions directly from the client</h2><p> Server actions allow you to run server-side functions directly from client components, creating a seamless bridge between frontend and backend code. </p></div><div class="_mb6_b6e01e"><h3 class="_sectionTitle_b6e01e">Core Features</h3><div class="_grid_b6e01e _grid3_b6e01e"><div class="_card_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">🔒</div><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Type Safe</h4><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> TypeScript type checking covers the complete call chain from client to server </p></div><div class="_card_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">🔄</div><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Auto Serialization</h4><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Automatically handles parameter and return value serialization, no manual conversion needed </p></div><div class="_card_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">📞</div><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Direct Call</h4><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Call server functions like local functions, no need to write API routes </p></div></div></div><div class="_infoPanel_b6e01e _success_b6e01e"><h3 class="_subsectionTitle_b6e01e">Interactive Demo</h3><p> Enter some text below. After clicking &quot;Send to Server&quot;, the text will be sent to the server-side function for processing, and return a response containing timestamp and server information. </p><div style="margin-top:1.5rem;"><web-widget import="/routes/examples/action/Echo@widget.tsx" name="Echo" loading="lazy" rendertarget="light" recovering><div class="_echoWidget_aa8e33"><form><div class="_inputGroup_aa8e33"><label for="echo-input" class="_label_aa8e33">💬 Enter Message</label><div class="_inputContainer_aa8e33"><input id="echo-input" type="text" placeholder="Enter any text, server will echo back the processed result..." class="_input_aa8e33" value=""/><button type="submit" class="_button_aa8e33" disabled="">📤 Send to Server</button></div></div></form></div></web-widget></div></div><div class="_comparison_b6e01e"><h3 class="_subsectionTitle_b6e01e _textCenter_b6e01e"> Comparison with Traditional API </h3><div class="_comparisonGrid_b6e01e"><div class="_comparisonItem_b6e01e"><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e" style="color:var(--color-error);margin-bottom:1rem;"> Traditional REST API </h4><ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;"><li>❌ Need to create separate API routes</li><li>⚙️ Manual request/response serialization</li><li>🔄 Client and server types easily get out of sync</li><li>🛠️ Need additional error handling and state management</li><li>🔗 URL paths and parameters prone to errors</li></ul></div><div class="_comparisonItem_b6e01e"><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e" style="color:var(--color-success);margin-bottom:1rem;"> Web Widget Server Actions </h4><ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;"><li>✅ Function is API, no additional routes needed</li><li>⚡ Auto serialization, no manual conversion</li><li>🔒 Complete TypeScript type safety</li><li>🎯 Built-in loading and error states</li><li>📞 Call like local functions</li></ul></div></div></div></div><!--]--></main><footer class="_footer_408c0a"><div class="_footerContent_408c0a"><div class="_footerBrand_408c0a"><h3 class="_footerBrandName_408c0a">Web Widget</h3><p class="_footerTagline_408c0a"> Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication </p></div><div class="_footerLinks_408c0a"><a href="https://github.com/web-widget/web-widget#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="_footerLink_408c0a"> 📚 Documentation </a><a href="https://github.com/web-widget/web-widget" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="_footerLink_408c0a"> ⭐ GitHub </a></div></div></footer><!--]-->
      </body>
    </html>"
`;

