"<!doctype html>
    <html lang="en">
      <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" /><title >Data Fetching - Web Widget</title><style >web-widget{display:contents}</style><script type="module" src="/@vite/client"></script><script type="module" src="/entry.client.ts"></script><script type="server:context">{"pathname":"/examples/fetch","params":{}}</script>
      </head>
      <body>
        <!--[--><a href="#main-content" class="skip-link"> Skip navigation, go to main content </a><header class="_header_408c0a"><div class="_headerContent_408c0a"><div class="_brandLogo_408c0a"><a class="_brandText_408c0a" href="/"> Web Widget </a><div class="_techStackBadge_408c0a"><span class="_techText_408c0a">Vue Example</span></div></div><nav class="_navigation_08e302" aria-label="Main navigation" role="navigation"><button class="_mobileMenuButton_08e302" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobile-navigation-menu" aria-label="Open navigation menu"><span class="_hamburgerIcon_08e302"><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span></span></button><ul id="mobile-navigation-menu" class="_navigationMenu_08e302" role="list" aria-hidden="true"><!--[--><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples" class="" aria-label="Home">Home</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/static" class="" aria-label="Static Page">Static Page</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/params/web-widget" class="" aria-label="Dynamic Routing">Dynamic Routing</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/fetch" class="" aria-label="Data Fetching">Data Fetching</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/action" class="" aria-label="Server Actions">Server Actions</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/frameworks" class="" aria-label="Widgets">Widgets</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/middleware" class="" aria-label="Middleware">Middleware</a></li><!--]--></ul><!-- Mobile menu background overlay --><!----></nav></div></header><main id="main-content" class="_main_408c0a" tabindex="-1"><!--[--><div class="_container_b6e01e"><h1 class="_pageTitle_b6e01e">🔄 Data Fetching</h1><div class="_highlight_b6e01e _info_b6e01e"><h2>Fetch data on the server and render as static HTML</h2><p> The following data is fetched on the server and rendered as static HTML. No need to wait for client-side loading and data requests, content is immediately visible. </p></div><div class="_mb6_b6e01e"><h3 class="_sectionTitle_b6e01e"> Benefits of Server-Side Data Fetching </h3><div class="_grid_b6e01e _grid3_b6e01e"><div class="_card_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">🔍</div><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">SEO Optimized</h4><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Search engines can directly index complete data content </p></div><div class="_card_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">📱</div><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Better User Experience</h4><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Especially suitable for mobile devices and slow network environments </p></div><div class="_card_b6e01e"><div class="_cardIcon_b6e01e">🛡️</div><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">Data Security</h4><p class="_cardDescription_b6e01e"> Sensitive API keys and logic only run on the server </p></div></div></div><div class="_infoPanel_b6e01e _success_b6e01e"><h3 class="_subsectionTitle_b6e01e">Demo Data</h3><p>The following data is fetched through server-side API calls:</p><div class="_grid_b6e01e _grid2_b6e01e" style="margin-top:1.5rem;"><!--[--><div class="_card_b6e01e"><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">console.log(&#39;hello world&#39;)</h4><p class="_textMuted_b6e01e" style="margin:0;"> Data item #1</p></div><div class="_card_b6e01e"><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">echo &quot;hello world&quot;</h4><p class="_textMuted_b6e01e" style="margin:0;"> Data item #2</p></div><div class="_card_b6e01e"><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">print(&#39;hello world&#39;)</h4><p class="_textMuted_b6e01e" style="margin:0;"> Data item #3</p></div><div class="_card_b6e01e"><h4 class="_cardTitle_b6e01e">println!(&quot;Hello, World&quot;)</h4><p class="_textMuted_b6e01e" style="margin:0;"> Data item #4</p></div><!--]--></div><div style="margin-top:1.5rem;"><p><strong>Data source:</strong><a href="/examples/api/hello" target="_blank" class="_link_b6e01e"> /api/hello </a></p><p class="_textMuted_b6e01e" style="font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:0.5rem;"> Click the link above to view the original API response data </p></div></div></div><!--]--></main><footer class="_footer_408c0a"><div class="_footerContent_408c0a"><div class="_footerBrand_408c0a"><h3 class="_footerBrandName_408c0a">Web Widget</h3><p class="_footerTagline_408c0a"> Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication </p></div><div class="_footerLinks_408c0a"><a href="https://github.com/web-widget/web-widget#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="_footerLink_408c0a"> 📚 Documentation </a><a href="https://github.com/web-widget/web-widget" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="_footerLink_408c0a"> ⭐ GitHub </a></div></div></footer><!--]-->
