        <!--[--><a href="#main-content" class="skip-link"> Skip navigation, go to main content </a><header class="_header_408c0a"><div class="_headerContent_408c0a"><div class="_brandLogo_408c0a"><a class="_brandText_408c0a" href="/"> Web Widget </a><div class="_techStackBadge_408c0a"><span class="_techText_408c0a">Vue Example</span></div></div><nav class="_navigation_08e302" aria-label="Main navigation" role="navigation"><button class="_mobileMenuButton_08e302" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobile-navigation-menu" aria-label="Open navigation menu"><span class="_hamburgerIcon_08e302"><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span></span></button><ul id="mobile-navigation-menu" class="_navigationMenu_08e302" role="list" aria-hidden="true"><!--[--><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples" class="" aria-label="Home">Home</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/static" class="" aria-label="Static Page">Static Page</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/params/web-widget" class="" aria-label="Dynamic Routing">Dynamic Routing</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/fetch" class="" aria-label="Data Fetching">Data Fetching</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/action" class="" aria-label="Server Actions">Server Actions</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/frameworks" class="" aria-label="Widgets">Widgets</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/middleware" class="" aria-label="Middleware">Middleware</a></li><!--]--></ul><!-- Mobile menu background overlay --><!----></nav></div></header><main id="main-content" class="_main_408c0a" tabindex="-1"><!--[--><div class="_container_b6e01e"><h1 class="_pageTitle_b6e01e">🧅 Middleware</h1><div class="_highlight_b6e01e _info_b6e01e"><h2>Web Widget Middleware System</h2><p> Middleware is a core component of Web Widget&#39;s routing system, allowing you to insert custom logic into the request processing pipeline. This page dynamically modifies page metadata through middleware, demonstrating the powerful capabilities of middleware. </p></div><div class="_mb6_b6e01e"><h3 class="_sectionTitle_b6e01e">Response Headers Demo</h3><div class="_infoPanel_b6e01e _warning_b6e01e"><h4>⚙️ Dynamically Modified Request Headers</h4><p> This page&#39;s middleware also adds custom response headers. You can observe through browser developer tools: </p><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:1.5rem;"><li><strong>Network panel</strong>: Check the <code>X-Powered-By</code> demo header </li></ul></div></div><div class="_mb6_b6e01e"><h3 class="_sectionTitle_b6e01e">Page Metadata Operations Demo</h3><div class="_infoPanel_b6e01e _success_b6e01e"><h4>🔧 Dynamically Modified Page Metadata</h4><p> The current page&#39;s <code>&lt;meta&gt;</code> tags and scripts are all dynamically modified through middleware: </p><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:1.5rem;"><li><strong>Description</strong>: Dynamically added SEO-friendly page description </li><li><strong>Keywords</strong>: Injected keywords like &quot;middleware, web widget, demo&quot; </li><li><strong>Dynamic Script</strong>: Injected a JavaScript code snippet (check browser console) </li></ul></div></div></div><!--]--></main><footer class="_footer_408c0a"><div class="_footerContent_408c0a"><div class="_footerBrand_408c0a"><h3 class="_footerBrandName_408c0a">Web Widget</h3><p class="_footerTagline_408c0a"> Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication </p></div><div class="_footerLinks_408c0a"><a href="https://github.com/web-widget/web-widget#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="_footerLink_408c0a"> 📚 Documentation </a><a href="https://github.com/web-widget/web-widget" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="_footerLink_408c0a"> ⭐ GitHub </a></div></div></footer><!--]-->
      </body>
    </html>"
`;

