      </head>
      <body>
        <!--[--><a href="#main-content" class="skip-link"> Skip navigation, go to main content </a><header class="_header_408c0a"><div class="_headerContent_408c0a"><div class="_brandLogo_408c0a"><a class="_brandText_408c0a" href="/"> Web Widget </a><div class="_techStackBadge_408c0a"><span class="_techText_408c0a">Vue Example</span></div></div><nav class="_navigation_08e302" aria-label="Main navigation" role="navigation"><button class="_mobileMenuButton_08e302" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobile-navigation-menu" aria-label="Open navigation menu"><span class="_hamburgerIcon_08e302"><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span><span class="_hamburgerLine_08e302"></span></span></button><ul id="mobile-navigation-menu" class="_navigationMenu_08e302" role="list" aria-hidden="true"><!--[--><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples" class="" aria-label="Home">Home</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/static" class="" aria-label="Static Page">Static Page</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/params/web-widget" class="" aria-label="Dynamic Routing">Dynamic Routing</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/fetch" class="" aria-label="Data Fetching">Data Fetching</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/action" class="" aria-label="Server Actions">Server Actions</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/frameworks" class="" aria-label="Widgets">Widgets</a></li><li role="listitem"><a href="/examples/middleware" class="" aria-label="Middleware">Middleware</a></li><!--]--></ul><!-- Mobile menu background overlay --><!----></nav></div></header><main id="main-content" class="_main_408c0a" tabindex="-1"><!--[--><div class="_container_b6e01e"><h1 class="_pageTitle_b6e01e">📄 Static Page</h1><div class="_highlight_b6e01e _info_b6e01e"><h2>Pure static HTML, no client-side JavaScript required</h2><p> This page is pure static HTML with no client-side interaction required. This means we don&#39;t need to load any JavaScript code. </p></div><div class="_mb6_b6e01e"><h3 class="_subsectionTitle_b6e01e">Features &amp; Benefits</h3><ul class="_featureList_b6e01e"><li><strong>Fast Loading</strong> - No need to wait for JavaScript download and execution </li><li><strong>SEO Friendly</strong> - Search engines can directly index complete content </li><li><strong>Low Resource Usage</strong> - Reduces client-side computation and battery consumption </li><li><strong>High Availability</strong> - Content displays normally even when JavaScript is disabled </li></ul></div><div class="_demoList_6e006e"><h3 class="_subsectionTitle_b6e01e">Verification Methods</h3><p> You can verify this is a pure static page through the following methods: </p><ol><li> Right-click to view page source - content is completely rendered in HTML </li><li> Open Developer Tools Network panel and refresh the page - no additional JavaScript requests </li><li> Disable JavaScript and refresh the page - content still displays completely </li></ol></div></div><!--]--></main><footer class="_footer_408c0a"><div class="_footerContent_408c0a"><div class="_footerBrand_408c0a"><h3 class="_footerBrandName_408c0a">Web Widget</h3><p class="_footerTagline_408c0a"> Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication </p></div><div class="_footerLinks_408c0a"><a href="https://github.com/web-widget/web-widget#readme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="_footerLink_408c0a"> 📚 Documentation </a><a href="https://github.com/web-widget/web-widget" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="_footerLink_408c0a"> ⭐ GitHub </a></div></div></footer><!--]-->
